{"tid":1263204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［毒酒］多款啤酒被驗出含除草劑致癌成分 青島殘留量最高","createTime":"2019-06-28T05:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T08:52:00.000Z","uid":31744,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bf48598a22d018e8ec7b3aed838386421e31badf","tid":1263204,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:08:07.000Z","msg":"啤酒是不少人小酌時的心頭好，但最近美國組織US PIRG檢驗了20個啤酒及餐酒的樣本，發現大部分啤酒都殘留了被列為二級致癌物的農藥成分草甘膦，當中包括常見的青島、百威及喜力啤酒。雖然研究指出所有樣本的殘留量並沒有超標，但US PIRG認為啤酒的健康風險仍值得關注。<br />\n<br />\n啤酒由大麥及小麥釀製而成，故此有機會殘留農藥成分，例如除草劑。<br />\n<br />\n據US PIRG的資料顯示，在20款啤酒及餐酒樣本之中，多達19款被檢測出含有來自除草劑的二級致癌物草甘膦。<br />\n<br />\n在啤酒樣本之中，青島啤酒被驗出草甘膦殘留量最高，含量為49.7ppb。其次為Coors Light，含量為31.1ppb。而大家熟悉的百威及喜力亦有上榜，分別為27ppb及20.9ppb。<br />\n<br />\n不過，US PIRG表示今次所檢測出的草甘膦殘留量並沒有超標。雖然含量不屬於危險水平，但啤酒健康風險依然值得關注。組織更提醒，人體攝取1ppt的草甘膦，有機會刺激乳癌細胞生長及干擾內分泌系統。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z8r2gSd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ8r2gSd.png&h=1457b2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CuMYzDU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCuMYzDU.png&h=60cc4e3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sMjfBSe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsMjfBSe.png&h=7713076e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DDYcD5A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDDYcD5A.png&h=73264f81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f20d21f5db85e3cd628cf816cdfe007850043ef3","tid":1263204,"uid":153329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T05:11:49.000Z","msg":"推！罷忍清倒"},{"pid":"ce9008e9ecd35b60601e9c2e799e6adeed9ea344","tid":1263204,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"班人仲幾打咁隊我真係笑而不語"},{"pid":"e3e22f6534ee607c81a87ec9202ab085fb34934d","tid":1263204,"uid":41311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:38:26.000Z","msg":"好彩飲嘉士伯"},{"pid":"5c37269f90b6b0324592b6f13242dc60b39f7c2a","tid":1263204,"uid":231111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"罷飲清島"},{"pid":"3bd55a1f9b3717c5d998e7d790101dfea03477e0","tid":1263204,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c78d819828c841300d3f65ce9a777ed03a23258","tid":1263204,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:48:26.000Z","msg":"啤酒=屎水"},{"pid":"3463d5dc417ab3f30a1350847a0e632f7369bb2d","tid":1263204,"uid":132572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"咁如果係係D麥上有農藥<br />\n咁麵粉都有啦 食麵都有啦<br />\n致唔致都好 罷飲青島"}]}